= \sum_{\tau}R(\tau)p_{\theta}(\tau)\nabla logp_{\theta}(\tau) 	\\
= \mathbb{E}_{\tau \sim p_{\theta}(\tau)}[R(\tau)\nabla logp_{\theta}(\tau)]
