Min(Loss) = Min(- \sum_{t=1}^{T} y_i \hat{y}_i) \\
= Max(\sum_{t=1}^{T} y_i p_{\theta}(a_t|s_t))	\\
\because y_i是常数1	\\
\therefore Min(Loss) = Max(\sum_{t=1}^{T} p_{\theta}(a_t|s_t)) = Max(\sum_{t=1}^{T} log p_{\theta}(a_t|s_t))
